CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 21, 1959, pg. A1 reads: "Nursery Opening - With Housing Authority Administrator Alfred L. Tronzo and Mrs. Valerie Watts, president of the sponsoring club (top left photo, third and fourth from left), women of Bedford Dwellings, known as Club 1213, opened a day nursery Monday...Top right photo shows little Donna Marie Lee reaching for one of the dozens of cookies baked by club members for the dedication ceremony...- Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Donna Marie Lee reaching for tray of cookies on buffet table with trays of sandwiches and punch bowl, at nursery opening in Bedford Dwellings
